{"tid":1989142,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"〔廣東話戰線〕想推廣東話嘅麻煩唔好撚再話廣東話好難！！","createTime":"2020-04-25T16:48:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T08:22:47.000Z","uid":115965,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7c781762a4fa4881c7ec533e0a49c15f8a1b318f","tid":1989142,"uid":115965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T16:48:14.000Z","msg":"我知大家好想區別廣東話同普通話，亦好想突顯廣東話嘅獨特性，<br />\n但當有外國人想學／學緊廣東話嘅時候，點解咁多香港人嘅feedback係「廣東話好難學」、「廣東話唔易學架」，真心唔明&hellip;依種講法除咗打飛機之外到底有乜撚野用？？<br />\n麻煩大家諗下點樣真係可以吸引人學廣東話！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如以下幾個方向（請自己因應對象調整）：<br />\n1.廣東話勝在有趣生動，多slang，廣東話流行文化（電影、電視、書、歌等等）亦有異於普通話<br />\n2.廣東話有6個聲調係難（唔計ptk），但文法冇日韓文咁複雜，多聽多講好易上手<br />\n3.繁體字、讀音保留中國傳統文化等唔洗係度多講<br />\n4.社交性，香港人好歡迎人學廣東話，識咗廣東話好容易識香港fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5.反共反極權但又對中國文化有興趣嘅人唔洗一定被逼學普通話，可以嚟學廣東話<br />\n6.識咗廣東話唔洗特登學都識普通話<br />\n以上為拋磚引玉，歡迎大家提出其他原因！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ngoogle一下都可以見到唔少外國人猶豫學普通話定廣東話，麻煩大家諗下自己會點答，「難」真係一個好嘅回應？<br />\n以後見到人學緊廣東話麻煩真係講啲鼓勵性／資訊性嘅嘢，而唔係作為一個native speaker話「廣東話好難架，加油！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可以參考下外國人學廣東話感想<br />\n<a href=\"https://fulltimefluency.com/2019/01/14/learn-cantonese/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffulltimefluency.com%2F2019%2F01%2F14%2Flearn-cantonese%2F&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCqVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=b85b9bdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fulltimefluency.com/2019/01/14/learn-cantonese/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.city-data.com/forum/asia/1789750-cantonese-most-difficult-hardest-language.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.city-data.com%2Fforum%2Fasia%2F1789750-cantonese-most-difficult-hardest-language.html&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCqVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=99c6b34d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.city-data.com/forum/asia/1789750-cantonese-most-difficult-hardest-language.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fluentin3months.com/cantonese/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fluentin3months.com%2Fcantonese%2F&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCqVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=a862700b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fluentin3months.com/cantonese/</a><br />\n<br />\n希望愈來愈多人對廣東話＋香港有興趣！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c24a7adc5974acdb7aafcd567ec0d57bab9942","tid":1989142,"uid":5005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T16:49:10.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全港最大良心飯券計劃正式上線啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1985553/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1985553/page/1</a><br />\n--------------------------------------------------------<br />\n不分化 不割席 不篤灰"},{"pid":"e017c97551ed80c00de04de8abee6cb94823bdfd","tid":1989142,"uid":5005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T16:49:23.000Z","msg":"幫你推多下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f59d344abe5fbbee451750464fdf1cf60586bcd","tid":1989142,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T16:51:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28a473f2ba4fe48f996824c42b12f00dbb1e194","tid":1989142,"uid":85751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T16:51:31.000Z","msg":"唔該大家唔好淨係以為全香港人都睇連登<br />\n<br />\n你要推就<br />\n1. push post<br />\n2. copy link<br />\n3. Share t